---
import Logo from './Logo.astro'
import Themetoggle from './Themetoggle.astro';
---

<header>
  <div class="fb items-center flex-row">
    <a href="." onclick="return false" hover:filter-brightness-120 transition-all>
      <Logo />
    </a>
    <Themetoggle />
  </div>
  <div class="fi mt-2 font-mono">
    <a href="." onclick="return false" select-none>
      <span class="gpt-subtitle dark:filter-sepia">chat</span><span class="gpt-title dark:gpt-subtitle dark:filter-invert">.bnu120.space</span>
    </a>
  </div>
  <p mt-1 font-light font-serif op-80 style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt;">
    <span op-40>如果你在找原来那个</span>
    <a b-slate-link href="//chat.academic.bnu120.space">ChatGPT 学术优化</a>
    <span op-40>网站，那个网站迁移到了</span><a b-slate-link href="//chat.academic.bnu120.space">chat.academic.bnu120.space</a>

    <span block h-2></span>

    <a font-bold b-slate-link href="https://cdn.muspimerol.site/free-chat-tips-01.html">如果你没用什么使用ChatGPT的经验，可以先看看教程➡️</a>

    <span block h-2></span>

    <span op-40>TIPS: 如果请求返回</span>
    <a b-slate-link href="https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/chat/managing-tokens">context_length_exceeded</a>
    <span op-40>的字样，那是因为上下文太长了，这是OpenAI对ChatGPT的限制</span>
  </p>
</header>
